text.__SUMMARY__:
Inga micheliana, known as the Cuajiniquil, Guaba De Montaña, Guajinicuil, or Jacanaquil, is a species of legume in the family Fabaceae.
It is found in Costa Rica, Guatemala, Honduras, Mexico, Nicaragua, and Panama.
